List of system areas
   (Both those which are explicit in the Prolog model, and those which are
hidden or implicitly in support of the model.)

Parser:

parser area		prs_area (areap)	alloc.c
parser stack		pstack			parser.c
string area		strarea			parser.c
token table		tktble			parser.c
initial tokens table	initoks			parser.c
variable names table	vtable			parser.c
error table		prs_erc			parser.c

WAM:

code area					wintcode.c
heap			the_heap		
